{"tid":2477773,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"[高達扭蛋/盒蛋討論區９] MSE / FORTE / FW# / G FRAME / NX / SDFC etc...","createTime":"2021-04-06T14:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T11:41:44.000Z","uid":165391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bfdd1679273f18f98975a14e557b7142a91bbb77","tid":2477773,"uid":165391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T14:14:54.000Z","msg":"上個POST <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2382628/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2382628/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n1. MOBILE SUIT ENSEMBLE[MSE]<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/a1vO2hE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fa1vO2hE.png&h=48a0c96e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官網: <a href=\"http://gashapon.jp/ensemble/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgashapon.jp%2Fensemble%2F&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=b116e355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://gashapon.jp/ensemble/</a><br />\n扭蛋系列 500円<br />\n魂限 EX/OPTION SET MORE<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n優點 - 可動性、組合度最高，高達版LEGO，上色/造型唔錯，有大量武器配件。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p-bandai.com/img/hk/p/m/N2578151001001_001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp-bandai.com%2Fimg%2Fhk%2Fp%2Fm%2FN2578151001001_001.jpg&h=d04a160e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p-bandai.com/img/hk/p/m/N2578150001001_013.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp-bandai.com%2Fimg%2Fhk%2Fp%2Fm%2FN2578150001001_013.jpg&h=6a46b3d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://bandai-a.akamaihd.net/bc/img/model/b/1000151022_5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbandai-a.akamaihd.net%2Fbc%2Fimg%2Fmodel%2Fb%2F1000151022_5.jpg&h=92b72d0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nEX22 TR-6 [銀雷 泰坦斯配色] 夢幻級別機體再商品化 淨係銀霤已經可以吹奏10年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n缺點 - 由於EX09/22太劃時代，價錢媲美PG、MB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一彈通常得3隻機體，要配合背包/武器包先玩到真正嘅MSE，甚至引你每款買複數重現唔同型態<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />17彈開始由全5款&gt;全款6隻，其中兩款1/2配率，變相加價，唔係成日行玩具場可以考慮預訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n系列踏入第4年，通販去到17彈，情報去到19彈，魂限EX已經30彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頭幾彈或者部份EX炒得貴到飛天，後追想制霸越黎越難，但同時有2.5/3.5/4.5換色復刻。<br />\n間中有少少偷膠，不過系列吸引力令所有玩家變M，入咗深淵難抽身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n2. 扭蛋戰士NEXT/DASH/FORTE<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.gashapon.jp/forte/images/top/img_mv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gashapon.jp%2Fforte%2Fimages%2Ftop%2Fimg_mv.png&h=bf059ad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://gashapon.jp/forte/images/items/ex004/img_ex04_01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgashapon.jp%2Fforte%2Fimages%2Fitems%2Fex004%2Fimg_ex04_01.png&h=bbffe39a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://gashapon.jp/forte/images/items/13/img_083.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgashapon.jp%2Fforte%2Fimages%2Fitems%2F13%2Fimg_083.jpg&h=8505e323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://bandai-a.akamaihd.net/bc/img/model/b/1000154893_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbandai-a.akamaihd.net%2Fbc%2Fimg%2Fmodel%2Fb%2F1000154893_1.jpg&h=c13d0a66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官網<br />\nFORTE: <a href=\"http://www.gashapon.jp/forte/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gashapon.jp%2Fforte%2F&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=a8b7e905\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.gashapon.jp/forte/</a><br />\nDASH: <a href=\"http://www.gashapon.jp/dash/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gashapon.jp%2Fdash%2F&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=1b1006e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.gashapon.jp/dash/</a><br />\nNEXT: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1Dmsd5d0g1AJ-BEnsS06HN9o8Na4CwRGR?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1Dmsd5d0g1AJ-BEnsS06HN9o8Na4CwRGR%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=2da0bb5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1Dmsd5d0g1AJ-BEnsS06HN9o8Na4CwRGR?usp=sharing</a><br />\n扭蛋系列 200円&gt;300円<br />\n魂限 P/SAGA/EX/EXTENSION SET MORE<br />\n3個系列屬繼承關係，NEXT&gt;DASH&gt;FORTE，同FW差唔多時間出<br />\n優點 - 2.5頭身比例比較貼合舊SD造型，而且關節比FW多，有一定可動性。機體種類雖不及FW，不過都算多，而且有唔少武者系列。<br />\n缺點 - 由於歷經3個系列，而其中造型/關節不斷改變，前期同後期欠奉統一性，NEXT22以後質素十分參差，DASH更加被FW屌打至8彈收皮。<br />\n扭蛋部更換負責人後FORTE開始有起色，但質素(F01後)仍然無提升，甚至限定都出事。新經理亦較著重親生仔MSE，<del>無熱水/風筒下，難砌到講粗口！</del>11彈開始部份關節兼容MSE，易砌咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遊艇仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2021預計得2-3彈，比幾個系列夾擊中，成本所限，偶有良作: F09 Z Plus、積根、F11突自、吉姆、F12 F13全彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓豬因為SDFC、NEXT情義結每彈仍然大量入手，各位FORTE同好共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nF14會有GP01、GP02A、吉姆CUSTOM、鎖暴型吉姆！鍾意量產嘅朋友可以繼續關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. FW GUNDAM CONVERGE[FW、FW#]<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ig4rHGL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fig4rHGL.png&h=4e5c5388&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官網: <a href=\"http://www.bandai.co.jp/candy/gundam/converge/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bandai.co.jp%2Fcandy%2Fgundam%2Fconverge%2F&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=fb6f30be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bandai.co.jp/candy/gundam/converge/</a><br />\n盒蛋系列 350円&gt;400円&gt;550円連稅、新通販line #Plus 990円連稅<br />\n魂限 部份EX/CORE/限定 MORE<br />\n優點 - 上色最靚、長壽系列機體種類多、CORE &amp; EX系列質素高。仲有開始有其他作品機體eg魯路修、裝甲騎兵、電腦戰機... 相關系列:RIDER/龍珠/STAR WAR...<br />\n食玩部新負責人108上場之後QC開始好返少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.bandai.co.jp/candy/gundam/converge/ex33/11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bandai.co.jp%2Fcandy%2Fgundam%2Fconverge%2Fex33%2F11.jpg&h=4f563a63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.bandai.co.jp/candy/gundam/converge/plus02/01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bandai.co.jp%2Fcandy%2Fgundam%2Fconverge%2Fplus02%2F01.jpg&h=e648408b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n缺點 - 站屍無乜可動性可言，無印出到20完，FW#將舊機砍掉重練，通販/EX加水印會變CORE再出一隻，部份通販機造型十分唔掂eg卡碧尼、Hi-Nu、F91...<br />\n樓豬無收此系列，唔可以作客觀評論，但純睇圖都覺得普遍MA、EX機、通販W五子幾好J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. G FRAME<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.bandai.co.jp/candy/gundam/gframe/images/point01pcJa.2007.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bandai.co.jp%2Fcandy%2Fgundam%2Fgframe%2Fimages%2Fpoint01pcJa.2007.jpg&h=3cc4d849&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.bandai.co.jp/candy/gundam/gframe/pb12/01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bandai.co.jp%2Fcandy%2Fgundam%2Fgframe%2Fpb12%2F01.jpg&h=13b0a858&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官網: <a href=\"https://www.bandai.co.jp/candy/gundam/gframe/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bandai.co.jp%2Fcandy%2Fgundam%2Fgframe%2F&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=7fceafeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bandai.co.jp/candy/gundam/gframe/</a><br />\n食玩系列 550円連稅、魂限SET<br />\n優點 - 因為有骨，可動性比MSE更高，武品配件都算多。3年就出咗13彈，算係食玩部進取嘅系列。兄弟系列EVA-FRAME，之後會有更多其他機械人系列產品。食玩部第2主力，由於FW人氣機出得7788，估計未來會係G FRAME同MSE爭天下。<br />\n缺點 - 每彈8款，4款固定骨+4款可動骨&amp;武器，其實1100円先砌到1隻完整機體，亦衍生大量雞肋固定骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ABS含量多，樓主覺得素組比較膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 其他系列<br />\n仲出緊:<br />\nROBOT CONCERTO [MSE原創機械人兄弟系列]<br />\n銷售手法幾嘔心，01彈換配色出咗5次(01, 夾夾機, 1.5, 日魂新黑金配色, 黑紫配色)<br />\nK澤<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再無新情報，下個POST已死系列又添一員<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://bandai-a.akamaihd.net/bc/img/model/b/1000154834_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbandai-a.akamaihd.net%2Fbc%2Fimg%2Fmodel%2Fb%2F1000154834_1.jpg&h=c14e499b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEXCEED MODEL 渣古頭/高達頭/大魔頭/鐵球/SD魔蟹 [一模多用究極體]<br />\n官網: <a href=\"https://gashapon.jp/exceedmodel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgashapon.jp%2Fexceedmodel%2F&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=106b5984\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gashapon.jp/exceedmodel/</a><br />\n<br />\n單色擦膠 [1985-now不定期翻炒經典]<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/E47On2zR_Vw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FE47On2zR_Vw&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=4f15e56d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/E47On2zR_Vw</a><br />\n<br />\n6. NXEDGE STYLE<br />\n<img src=\"https://tamashii.jp/images/category_ui/MTWMVz08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftamashii.jp%2Fimages%2Fcategory_ui%2FMTWMVz08.jpg&h=11bea8b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官網: <a href=\"https://tamashii.jp/item_brand/nxedge/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftamashii.jp%2Fitem_brand%2Fnxedge%2F&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=5b0e8257\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tamashii.jp/item_brand/nxedge/</a><br />\n成品部6年半長壽系列，初代負責人由盒蛋部調職過黎，所以有幾分FW味道，由於樓主有儲公海無乜post，所以放埋佢入黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"gold\">邊度買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n油麻地(現時點)、旺角(信和、兆萬 )、灣仔(太原街)、深水埗福利etc<br />\n皆旺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個場半死咁濟 可以慳返D腳骨力<br />\n<br />\n預訂日魂限定<br />\n孤仔、古迦、五月 - 連鎖店<br />\nNewAge、歷奇 - 多數得普通彈</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"violet\">黑名單<br />\n藍店: 明眼人 精_品玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBuy-ee日本代購 垃撚圾客服 價錢貴服務差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>砌到手指痛點好?<br />\n風筒/熱水/其他工具補助會易砌D</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n洗扭蛋盒蛋可以參考 (樓主有個$200平價貨 頻率低好多 for洗塵OK)<br />\n平價清塵<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZoXqPPvgagU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZoXqPPvgagU&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=2627830d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZoXqPPvgagU</a><br />\n<br />\n貴價洗油<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iiz-9DkreZQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Diiz-9DkreZQ&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=011c3b9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iiz-9DkreZQ</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位同好繼續討論<br />\n買賣／交換請自行交換聯絡方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d78980831537f12703de1d324711378ef475219","tid":2477773,"uid":165391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T14:15:36.000Z","msg":"已死系列:<br />\nSD GUNDAM FULL COLOR [SDFC 1997-2006經典]<br />\n斎藤勝巴打提供嘅蛋紙<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1uywS8htxfUPW6EZlNixf3fDQUQbdxXoB?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1uywS8htxfUPW6EZlNixf3fDQUQbdxXoB%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=98f87dbc\" data-a